race.comment: RADAR'S PATROL (2) turned spotting a big start finishing sixth (26.65) last time in a Grade 5 at this track. Form at the trip sound including two wins. Has ability and is a key runner. WARDEN OZZIE (1) turned in a solid run last start over 460m at this track finishing 5th and beaten only 4.5 lengths (26.72). Has a good record here at this journey. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. NICKY BOO BOO (7) has missed the frame at his last couple but wasn't beaten far three back when second (23.27) at this track in a Grade 5. Can turn it around this time. BUST UP (8) is in the mix after placing last time out.
